products.title: MSI Gaming GeForce RTX 2060 6GB GDRR6 192-bit HDMI/DP Ray Tracing Turing Architecture VR Ready Graphics Card (RTX 2060 Ventus 6G OC)
features: Video memory: 6gb gddr6. Power consumption: 190 w
products.description: A fresh new dual fan design, VENTUS proudly displays its industrial shapes in neutral colors to fit any build. Using two of the award-winning TORX Fans 2. 0, MSI VENTUS graphics cards provide years of top-notch cooling performance. Up to 6mm thick copper heat pipes at the bottom maximize heat transfer from the surface of the copper base plate.
